OL,6,FWe can talk another time about whether
OL,7,Fthis rule is sensible or Dali-esque
OL,8,Fnonsense. It is what it is.JIf Hunt is
OL,9,Fcontent with #6 billion of headroom,
OL,10,Fhe would have #7 billion to deploy to
OL,11,Fhis political preference of cutting
OL,12,Ftaxes on income or enough for just a
OL,13,Fpenny off the basic rate of income
OL,14,Ftax. A 1p cut in the rate of employee
OL,15,Fnational insurance would be #2 billion
OL,16,Fa year cheaper.JHowever, and as I've
OL,17,Fpointed out, it would be a political
OL,18,Fdisaster for both Hunt and Rishi Sunak
OL,19,Fto deliver income tax cuts as small as
OL,20,Fthat. All their political rhetoric for
OL,21,Fweeks has been about the urgency of
OL,22,Fdoing more.
