OL,6,FIt would also be relatively less
OL,7,Fvaluable to those earning more than
OL,8,F#50,000 a year, a demographic the
OL,9,FTories want and need to woo, than a
OL,10,Fcut in the basic rate of income tax
OL,11,Fwould be.JMy hunch, therefore, is that
OL,12,FHunt will announce a penny off each,
OL,13,Fat a cost of #12 billion a year.JThat
OL,14,Fwould leave him with #6 billion for
OL,15,Fassorted other measures, including
OL,16,Fperhaps a long-awaited tax break for
OL,17,Finvesting in UK companies via a new
OL,18,Fmore generous form of ISA.
